author: geirm
msg: Changed the binding of <whitespace><newline> for the end of directive statements to allow for leading whitespace in an inline block.  Ex #foreach($a in $array) $a#end will have a ' ' before each rendered $a. Previously, they were being sucked into the directive node to allow 'what you expect' behavior when you do a conventional #foreach() block.
